<article class="flex flex-col gap-4">
  <h1 class="text-4xl">Jamie Gordon</h1>

  <div class="flex md:flex-row flex-col gap-4">
    <%= vite_image_tag('images/Welcome.jpg', class: 'md:h-72 drop-shadow-xl') %>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <p>
        Hey, welcome!
      </p>
      <p>I've been coding since high school and professionally since 2013. In my career, I've been focused primarily in Ruby on Rails, with standard HTML/CSS frontends and React frontends.</p>
      <p>I also have some professional experience in Elixir, focusing more with parallel processing and data warehousing.</p>
      <p>Extensively used 3rd party APIs to connect to external services, as well as developing APIs for other companies to connect to.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl">Skills</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
      <li>Elixir</li>
      <li>React</li>
      <li>Typescript</li>
      <li>CSS, SCSS, all that style stuff</li>
      <li>HTML</li>
      <li>LaTeX (for Resume)</li>
      <li>Java (high school/college)</li>
      <li>External APIs (xml, json, you name it, I've probably dealt with it)</li>
      <li>Plus a bunch of other stuff</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl">Projects</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <h3 class="text-2xl">This site</h3>
      <%= link_to("https://github.com/gellaho/jamiesgordon.com", "https://github.com/gellaho/jamiesgordon.com", class: 'text-blue-700') %>
      <p>Ruby on Rails. Not a lot to see, mostly just shows off front end skills. Built using Tailwind.css and Alpine.js</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <h3 class="text-2xl">Discord Archive Creator (Elixir)</h3>
      <%= link_to('https://github.com/gellaho/book_cage', "https://github.com/gellaho/book_cage", class: 'text-blue-700') %>
      <p>Elixir. This is built for my other personal website, which archives book readings that I've done on Discord.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <h3 class="text-2xl">One English Word</h3>
      <%= link_to('oneenglishword.com', oneenglishword_path, class: 'text-blue-700') %>
      <p>A silly website that uses an API to show one English word at a time. Comes from an old inside joke.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</article>
